<div class="CV hresume">
  <h1>CV</h1>

  <h2 class="u-isHiddenVisually">Profile</h2>
  <p class="u-textLead summary">I've been building websites professionally for
    over seven years and I specialise in HTML, CSS and JavaScript.</p>

  <h2 id="employment">Employment</h2>

  <% data.jobs.each do |job| %>
    <div class="u-mb20 u-pb20">
      <%= partial 'job', locals: { job: job } %>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <h2 id="skills">Skills</h2>
  <ul class="u-listUnstyled">
    <% data.skills.each do |skill| %>
      <li class="Skill u-inlineBlock"><%= skill.name %></li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="additional">Additional Information</h2>

  <p>Creating, owning and maintaining a hugely popular gaming community -
    <a href="http://www.interlopers.net">www.interlopers.net</a>. Since 2004 the site
    received thousands of page visits per day and has an expanding community of
    nearly 10,000 members.</p>

  <p>I have begun re-writing the entire site using the <a
  href="http://laravel.com">Laravel framework</a>. A preview of the
    responsive re-design can be viewed at <a
  href="http://stage.interlopers.net">stage.interlopers.net</a>.</p>

  <p>Acted as a reviewer for <a href="https://twitter.com/tbrd">Tom Hamshere</a>'s
    book on <a href="http://goo.gl/DznlPd">Twitter's Flight library</a>. This
    involved communicating with the book editors and suggesting edits and code
    changes.</p>

  <h2 id="interests">Interests</h2>

  <p>I play drums in <a href="http://fashodacrisis.com">a loud rock band</a>.
    We've completed three tours of Eastern Europe and released multiple CDs
    independently.</p>

  <p>I've also had the remarkable experience of
    <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/simonblink24/sets/72157625051285708/">
      visiting Chernobyl in September 2010
    </a> and returning radiation free! A bit
    different to <i>‘Badminton, socialising and reading blogs’</i> usually found
    here!</p>
</div>